A vintage 1960s-style illustration of a team of professionals gathered around a large wooden table in a warm, wood-paneled library, examining towering stacks of documents and thick reference books. Filing cabinets with overflowing folders line the walls. One person holds up a magnifying glass over an architectural blueprint of a building. The color palette features muted oranges, browns, and creams with subtle paper texture throughout. The scene conveys collaborative knowledge work and the careful process of organizing and migrating vast amounts of information. Through a frosted window, the silhouette of a university campus building is visible, suggesting an academic setting in New England.
